trans-unit.source: Provides design-time support in a visual designer for the <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.Login"></xref> Web-server control.
trans-unit.target: Gir støtte for utforming i en visuelle utformeren for den <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.Login"> </xref> nettserveren kontroll.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Login> control displays a user interface that allows a user to log on to the host Web site.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Login>kontrollen viser et brukergrensesnitt som kan brukeren logge på webområdet verten.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Login>

trans-unit.source: In a visual designer, when you switch from Source to Design view, the markup source code that describes the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Login> control is parsed and a design-time version of the control is created on the design surface.
trans-unit.target: I en visuelle utformeren når du bytter fra kilden til utformingsvisning markup kildekode som beskriver den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Login>kontrollen analyseres og en utformingen versjon av kontrollen er opprettet på utformingsoverflaten.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Login>

trans-unit.source: When you switch back to Source view, the design-time control is persisted to the markup source code and edited into the markup for the Web page.
trans-unit.target: Når du går tilbake til visning i datakilden, er utformingen kontrollen beholdt i markup kildekode og redigeres i markup for websiden.

trans-unit.source: The LoginDesigner class provides design-time support for the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Login> control.
trans-unit.target: Klassen LoginDesigner gir støtte for utforming for den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Login>kontroll.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Login>

trans-unit.source: - The <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.LoginDesigner.AutoFormats%2A> property returns a collection of formatting schemes for display in the **Auto Format** dialog box.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Login.LayoutTemplate%2A> property of the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Login> control can be serialized using the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.LoginDesigner.GetEditableDesignerRegionContent%2A> method.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Login.LayoutTemplate%2A>for den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Login>kontrollen kan serialiseres ved hjelp av den <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.LoginDesigner.GetEditableDesignerRegionContent%2A>metoden.</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.LoginDesigner.GetEditableDesignerRegionContent%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Login> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Login.LayoutTemplate%2A>

trans-unit.source: An <xref href="System.Web.UI.Design.EditableDesignerRegion"></xref> that provides the name of the region to update.
trans-unit.target: En <xref href="System.Web.UI.Design.EditableDesignerRegion"> </xref> som inneholder navnet på området til å oppdatere.

trans-unit.source: A string that contains a serialized template for the associated control.
trans-unit.target: En streng som inneholder en serialisert mal for den tilknyttede kontrollen.

trans-unit.source: Gets a collection of template groups for the fields of the associated control.
trans-unit.target: Henter en samling av malen grupper for feltene for den tilknyttede kontrollen.

trans-unit.source: The TemplateGroups property gets a <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.TemplateGroupCollection> object from the TemplateGroups base property, and then adds a <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.TemplateGroup> object that contains a single <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.TemplateDefinition> object for the layout template of the associated <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Login> control to the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.TemplateGroupCollection>.
trans-unit.target: Egenskapen TemplateGroups henter et <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.TemplateGroupCollection>objekt fra egenskapen TemplateGroups base og legger til et <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.TemplateGroup>objekt som inneholder ett enkelt <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.TemplateDefinition>objekt for malen oppsettet for den tilknyttede <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Login>kontrollen <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.TemplateGroupCollection>.</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.TemplateGroupCollection> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Login> </xref:System.Web.UI.Design.TemplateDefinition> </xref:System.Web.UI.Design.TemplateGroup> </xref:System.Web.UI.Design.TemplateGroupCollection>

trans-unit.source: The TemplateGroups property returns this <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.TemplateGroupCollection> to the caller.
trans-unit.target: Egenskapen TemplateGroups returnerer dette <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.TemplateGroupCollection>til oppkalleren.</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.TemplateGroupCollection>

trans-unit.source: A <xref href="System.Web.UI.Design.TemplateGroupCollection"></xref> containing an element for each templated field in the <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.Login"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: En <xref href="System.Web.UI.Design.TemplateGroupCollection"> </xref> som inneholder et element for hvert organisasjonsapper felt i den <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.Login"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: Gets a value indicating whether the designer should use a temporary copy rather than the actual control associated with the designer to generate the design-time markup.
trans-unit.target: Henter en verdi som angir om designer må bruke en midlertidig kopi i stedet for den faktiske kontrollen som er forbundet med designer til å generere utformingen markup.

trans-unit.source: Because the UsePreviewControl property is always `true`, the designer <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ControlDesigner.ViewControl%2A> property returns a copy of the associated <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Login> control to generate the design-time markup.
trans-unit.target: Fordi egenskapen UsePreviewControl alltid `true`, designer <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ControlDesigner.ViewControl%2A>egenskapen returnerer en kopi av det tilknyttede <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Login>kontrollen til å generere utformingen markup.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Login> </xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ControlDesigner.ViewControl%2A>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ControlDesigner.ViewControl%2A> property creates the copy by persisting the actual <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Login> control, then parsing the persisted control string.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ControlDesigner.ViewControl%2A>egenskapen oppretter kopien av persisting den faktiske <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Login>kontrollen, og deretter analyse faste kontroll-streng.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Login> </xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ControlDesigner.ViewControl%2A>

trans-unit.source: The copied control does not affect any persistence for the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Login>.
trans-unit.target: Kopierte kontrollen påvirker ikke noen utholdenhet for <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Login>.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Login>

trans-unit.source: If the UsePreviewControl property has been overridden to return `false`, the designer uses the associated <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Login> itself to generate the design-time markup, and design-time changes to the control will persist to the page markup source.
trans-unit.target: Hvis egenskapen UsePreviewControl er overstyrt for å returnere `false`, designer bruker den tilknyttede <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Login>selve å generere utformingen markup, og endre utformingen kontrollen vil beholde siden markup kilde.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Login>
